# 内容：欧美直播、视频托管及 IPTV 深度 CDN 梳理版
# 更新：2025-01-25
# 逻辑：按核心分发网络 (CDN) 维度梳理，确保视频流、静态资源和播放接口全路径走专线

# ============================================================
# 1. 核心直播流分发网络 (Live Streaming CDNs)
# ============================================================

# --- Chaturbate 体系 (核心：mmcdn) ---
# 承载了 CB 绝大部分的实时视频流和直播间预览
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mmcdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cbstatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chaturbate.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,mmcdn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,chaturbate

# --- Stripchat 体系 (核心：doppiocdn) ---
# 它是 Stripchat、XhamsterLive 及其家族站点的核心传输网
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,doppiocdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,strpst.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stripchat.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,xhamsterlive.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,doppiocdn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stripchat

# --- Bongacams & Camsoda 体系 ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bngcdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bongacams.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,camsoda.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,bngcdn

# --- MyFreeCams 体系 ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mfcimg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,myfreecams.com

# ============================================================
# 2. 视频托管与高动态集群 (Video Hosting & Storage Clusters)
# ============================================================

# --- Vidplay / MyVidPlay 家族集群 ---
# 该集群特点是后缀极多，且使用大量动态产生的子域名进行分流
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,myvidplay.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mvidplay.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.online
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.site
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.to
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.biz
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.info
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.pro
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.icu
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.vip
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.cc
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidplay.org
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,vidplay
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,myvidplay

# --- DoodStream 集群 (多区域 CDN 负载) ---
# Dood 拥有庞大的自建节点，后缀包含大量地域性缩写，确保捕捉到所有视频传输域名
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,doodstream.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ds2play.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ds2video.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.so
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.la
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.wf
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.cx
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.sh
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.li
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.pm
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.ws
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.video
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.to
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.re
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.yt
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.watch
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.stream
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.tf
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dood.cc
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,dood

# --- Streamtape & Stape 集群 ---
# 其 CDN 节点通常以 stape 开头，对 IP 质量要求极高
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,streamtape.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stape.one
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stape.video
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stape.site
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stape.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,streamtape.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,streamadblock.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,streamtape
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stape

# --- MixDrop / Voe / UpStream / Vidmoly (混合第三方集群) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mixdrop.co
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mixdrop.to
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mixdrop.ag
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mixdrop.sx
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,voe.sx
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,voe-network.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,upstream.to
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vidmoly.me
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,mixdrop

# ============================================================
# 3. IPTV 与 电视广播传输 (IPTV & Global Delivery)
# ============================================================

# --- GoodIPTV (Vidhub 关键流地址) ---
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,goodiptv

# --- 通用 IPTV 分发关键字 ---
# 捕获那些隐藏在 m3u8 列表中的直接流域名
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,iptv
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stream-link
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,m3u8-delivery

# ============================================================
# 4. 通用关键词与 CDN 兜底 (Generic Identifiers)
# ============================================================
# 关键说明：mmcdn (Chaturbate) 和 doppiocdn (Stripchat) 是最重要的视频流 CDN。
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,mmcdn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,doppiocdn
# camstatic: 用于直播站点的封面、JS 加载
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,camstatic
# stream-content: 常见的第三方加速镜像
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stream-content
